[34m│[0m ### Python Pickle                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Indicators:**                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Base64 starting with `gASV`                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - Binary starting with `80 04 95`                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m - `.pickle` files                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Basic RCE payload:**                                                       [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```python                                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m import pickle                                                                [34m│[0m
