[34m│[0m ### Serialization Format Identification                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | Language/Format | Header (Hex)   | Header (Base64) | Indicators            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m |                                                                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m |-----------------|----------------|-----------------|---------------------- [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m -----|                                                                       [34m│[0m
